# Fullstack Shopping Cart – Hiring Assessment

This project is a small full-stack e-commerce shopping portal built for a hiring assessment.

Flow:
User → Login → View Items → Add Items to Cart → Checkout → Order

The backend is implemented in Go (Gin framework) with JSON file storage.
The frontend is a React application with a premium-style shopping UI.

---

## Tech Stack

Backend
• Go (Golang)
• Gin Web Framework
• JSON file database (db.json)
• Token-based authentication
• CORS enabled

Frontend
• React (Create React App)
• JavaScript ES6
• Custom CSS for premium UI
• Fetch API for backend communication

---

## Project Structure

ecommerce-assessment/
├── backend/
│   ├── main.go
│   ├── handlers.go
